Ok I have this guy friend lets say his name is ....Tim.Anyways we have been friends for
4 years and every year except for this year Tim has asked me out . I have said no a lot of times
except for when we went to the movies with a lot of our other friends together.
Now as i said above he hasnt asked me out any this year and hes acting nicer 
then ever to me. I actually think i like him as more then a friend now. One problem 
he has a girlfriend that dislikes me A LOT, and hes always around her and everything.
I havent told any of my friends about this because he likes to bug them and thinks they are
annoying and they think hes ugly and mean, but they know hes my friend and  they all 
respect that . Also today soemthing happened and it actually looked like we were holding hands.
So now my friends were teasing me and saying funny things and everything and one of  Tim's friends
said "your girlfriends gonna love this." Now I am afraid she might find out and dislike me more.
I keep trying to tell myself that I dont like him and I need to get over him because i just 
probaly want attention and miss him being my best friend and head over hills for me.

so any advice at all on anything?

My NASHVILLE REVIEW!!!!!!!!!!!
                   8.10.06 the best day evah

ok so my parents check me out at 12:00 to go to Nashville
to hopefully meet Ace and to go to the concert.After two hours of traveilng 
and getting lost once we get there.We walked around the building once then a woman stopped us 
and said we missed Ace and Chris were here 5 minutes ago in that spot i was standing.When she told me that
i didnt know if i wanted to cry or be mad lol.So we walked around about 30 more minutes and went and got something to eat
at macdonalds.There were alot of police there ...wierd, but everytime a fat police passed my brother he said "oink" behind them
it was hilariuos!Anyways we go back and never get to meet Ace so we just hang out there till 6:00 when the line started getting longer.
The news channel came and taped me it was funny we were all scrunched in and they told me to smile so i did that was awesome.
So we finally get in and get seated then the concert starts.


Mandisa comes out first and sings I cant tell you what she sung i was in Ace lala land.
Finally Ace came out and sung with Mandisa It was Excellent i loved it ace and her have amazing voices that
sounded great together!

Now Ace time!I didnt shutup i was screaming my heart out during the whole thing.
At the begining ace did this awesome chest throb thing i was drooling lol.After that he took his
jacket off and i was spazzing and sweating and yeah so my dad gives me a wierd look when i screamed "i want ace now!". Then he 
had the whole place standing up!After father figure Ace stands there for a second 
and then says "you people are amazing its raining like crazy" He was just laughing and laughing.
Then Harder to Breathe started and well the song title explains me i thought i was gonna cry or passout i loved it
he jumped off the rampy thingy and i was like"oh no dont do that again!".Well he doesnt jump agian but he puts he feet on the
rails and stands i was like"ur gonna give me a heart attack" but all i did was keep screaming and waving my beanie.

umm skipping the other peeps and going to paitence.

Patience was awesome im the biggest Axl Rose fan and at first i had doubts but
i thought ace did the best out of the group it was amazing!

Now We Are The Champions
On this song chris started it out then ace came out singing in falsetto!
I was standing up jumping waving my beanie around because we didnt have floor seats
so i didnt think ace could see me but we were first row from the floor.
Then Ace points over to my section and dumb me i turn around
and look for who he is pointing at but then i relize that im the only ace fan in my section LOL.
So then ace does a small wave at my section again and i dont wave cause im singing along with taylor i think
was singing at the time.So I start waving my beanie again in the hair.Then Ace starts doing a big wave in like the same way i 
was waving my beanie.Well that got my attention i figured out it was me he was waving at me so i finally wave.
Ace laughs and goes and does another smaller jump in a way idk i cant really figure out what it was LOL.After that was the other group song which 
i loved ace was really spazzy which was cool he was soo different. 
  
ill try to post the pics later but the r sorta black i couldnt stay still!
same for video but i zoomed out instead of in on it lol!
